quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"May the hands of Abu Lahab perish, and may he perish!"
  111,2,"Neither his wealth nor his worldly gains will avail him."
  111,3,"He will burn in a Flaming Fire,"
  111,4,"and so will his wife, the carrier of firewood,"
  111,5,"around her neck will be a rope of palm fiber."
